d0e102c451d62b66.voiceContent: What mein Fräulein means to say is that most of the literature in this study is of interest to her.

9ebc99477c3a3b4f.voiceContent: Who would've thought that one might find such a study outside the treasure trove of the magus-custodian of books...? It is worthy of one's extended stay, and may invoke seven blessings of the Prinzessin out of ten!

ed546b87cadf62f9.voiceContent: Hee-hee! One has witnessed how you have poured your heart and soul into the pursuit of the heavens and Abyssal Moon.

5f465c074870785f.voiceContent: Mein Fräulein means that she enjoys the style of adventurer camps. She never grows tired of it.

7d103d7efe931c96.voiceContent: Travelers, their appetite for adventure insatiable... Surely do they leave the most brilliant marks upon this paradise.

bed2298e70d530a8.voiceContent: Traveler from beyond, the sovereign Prinzessin shall arbitrate the discord of thine heart!

295d7773e53bf76f.voiceContent: Stalled have I the inexorable march of time and veiled the omnipresent gaze of fate.

08c4be92f135ac93.voiceContent: Tremors erupting from the earth are the dying echoes of an ancient god's heart.

946cc020dc2f0caa.voiceContent: What mein Fräulein means to say is...

744e08309b852943.voiceContent: Hmph. No mortal lifetime bears the imagination required to fathom the collective phenomena experienced by the Prinzessin.

17e44384f4e811e9.voiceContent: Preposterous! I am the Prinzessin der Verurteilung! What mortal follies could venture to imprint themselves upon my psyche?

9ba483ebde0df53b.voiceContent: When I was out on reconnaissance, didn't the new recruits from the Adventurers' Guild joke about you since they couldn't understand what you were saying?

f6a3855b44b39d12.voiceContent: Nonsense! How could I be perturbed by such trifling antics from my retinue?

2687d4928295bdc5.voiceContent: Feebly does the expanse that appears before me endeavor to capture my attention.

09f9da4b274ddbac.voiceContent: For a mortal domicile, it offers a modicum of respite.

2721434733ded385.voiceContent: Allay all doubt, for you are the one that I, the Prinzessin, have personally appointed. Hesitate not and proclaim my decrees to this world's denizens!

e78500694102eb94.voiceContent: Very good! Allow me to offer resplendent blessings to illuminate your fated travels!

2ae1a8a42fcd2c3f.voiceContent: This place is but a grain of sand in the shadow of my Immernachtreich.

9e7090ad7cfe5ffc.voiceContent: Stars cast from the celestial tapestry are the final moments of an hourglass.

5b25a5c061b416ee.voiceContent: By my regard, should Oz be conducting reconnaissance on my behalf, I grant you permission to remain in my propinquity.

e04907b821376af7.voiceContent: Now, relay the will of the Prinzessin to her attendants!

4c0630ce5e01cd40.voiceContent: You... Would you accompany me to witness this world's end and greet the descension of eternal night?

a31440996ff921a7.voiceContent: The furtive shades of our destinies intertwine themselves beneath hallowed light. Should tenebrous forces obscure thine path, you may call out my name in humble supplication.

f9f4fed0b29c2957.voiceContent: Along with my familiar of the night, Ozvaldo Hrafnavins, will safeguard your path ahead, for fate has revealed to me that this be decreed!

7d26e364aee69a75.voiceContent: Yes, indeed do I perceive rightly...

378ad01dce8fb7c9.voiceContent: Frankly, I also think this is a good idea.

a0af42b82a39f244.voiceContent: But mein Fräulein, you previously said that you wished to stay here for a while.

fb33a96cf21923e4.voiceContent: The one who perceives the truth and meaning of my declarations.

7897f7530183265b.voiceContent: Alas, I lament that those neophytes lack semblance to you, traveler from an outer world, the one delivered before me by the threads of fate.

774e9737fa7895ab.voiceContent: Rejoice! That wanton brume of devilry hath dissipated beneath my immaculate radiance!

7419a2a4816e449f.voiceContent: Mein Fräulein says, Good night. May you have sweet dreams.

cc16b68a53d4d9a2.voiceContent: I behold the magnificent vistas of three thousand worlds and am intimately acquainted with the threads of past and future.

164b11f41e5cf6f2.voiceContent: If there is something on your mind, she is happy to listen.

83d88c9b31e1ec8a.voiceContent: Shall I usher in this world's desolate finale with none save my own shadow?

7ea5d89a9c525685.voiceContent: Mein Fräulein says, Good morning, the sun is quite fine today. If you encounter any difficulties, please call for me.

4810effb14909dd5.voiceContent: What mein Fräulein means is that she happens to be free right now.

8178092f36e465a0.voiceContent: Dost thou wish to present any tidings to the Prinzessin before thee?

d95dd6781eb6e115.voiceContent: Profess tribute, for this space is exalted by my consecration. None shall interfere with your repose.

89bb3624d67d8108.voiceContent: I remember that you were distressed about this, mein Fräulein.

55331f820a664456.voiceContent: Oz No rest for the wicked...

90c9b1a117ced429.voiceContent: Wings of Darkness, come, sever night from day!

7419178914ffe624.voiceContent: Oz As you wish, mein Fräulein!

a6f2a51010883b07.voiceContent: What trinkets lie veiled within this desolate plane?

4de083198c754d7e.voiceContent: Hahaha, cry out my illustrious name!

534c6b6dbbc8a5cf.voiceContent: Oz Mein Fräulein, your presence is urgently required...

f66fd2b0dafc6fad.voiceContent: This realm is no home for a princess...

fe7c19d6cc49b805.voiceContent: In the name of the Prinzessin!

a409fbce9d8721e2.voiceContent: Oz Behold, the Prinzessin der Verurteilung!

4ea96dc792e37a2b.voiceContent: The threads of your fate lie in my hands!

8edfa6a517b4c128.voiceContent: Fischl I, Fischl, Prinzessin der Verurteilung, descend upon this land by the call of fate an— Oh, you are also a traveler from another world? Very well, I grant you permission to travel with me.Oz She means, Nice to meet you.

9702ed4a98f206d6.voiceContent: I hear the voice of fate, speaking my name in humble supplication...

07471b53653e4c39.voiceContent: Hm-hm, may the glory of the Prinzessin bring light to this world.

8223c15ba5bb05b8.voiceContent: Fischl I do worry about the well-being of my retinue during my impromptu absence...Oz I'm sure the good people of the Adventurers' Guild are absolutely fine, mein Fräulein.

dfc6e384e734d975.voiceContent: Oh, the sun's out— Oh, um... This meteorological transformation is most splendid! Like a felicitous twist of fate in the face of certain doom.

e657bf5e633657d3.voiceContent: Fischl Hark! 'Tis Thundering Retribution, an omen of dark times ahead...Oz That, and mein Fräulein's laundry is still on the line...Fischl Wha... Seriously!?

43401587e18348b7.voiceContent: Fischl A wonderful sight indeed. Why, it reminds me of my home world, where at the sight of the Prinzessin der Verurteilung, the very blood and tears of sinners turn to ice! ...Achoo! Achoo!Oz Not only their blood and tears, but also their saliva and mucus, mein Fräulein.Fischl Oz— Ahh—Achoo!!!

10f8b79a1ece1882.voiceContent: Fischl Ozzie, my dear familiar...Oz Ozzie? What's gotten into you...Fischl Her Majesty beseeches you to unfurl your blessèd wings, and with them blot out the heavens, plunging the world into eternal night...Oz If you didn't bring your parasol with you, that's your own fault, mein Fräulein!

7311758bb579649a.voiceContent: Dusk and dawn but fleeting shadows are. Once more, the twists of fate have led you into my everlasting night.

52bf6b037cd7af2a.voiceContent: Oz Good morning. Mein Fräulein heard you'd be dropping by, so she's preparing breakfast.Fischl Oz! ...Ahem. To what do I owe the pleasure?

4394316886aab436.voiceContent: Even one of royal blood finds oneself susceptible to drowsiness at this hour.

98c86bb143153c40.voiceContent: Fischl The stars of firmament are naught but rifts, thrust open by Oz's beak into the boundless tapestry of darkness.Oz You do say the strangest things, mein Fräulein.

94708dba29104e57.voiceContent: Fischl Me? Hehehe. Remember thou this, that I, Fischl, am the Prinzessin der Verurteilung, Sovereign of Immernachtreich, omniscient and eminent judge of all the world's iniquity!Oz She's an investigator for the Adventurers' Guild.Fischl ...Ahem. That is but one of my many royal engagements.

6c2b1c79a7735e07.voiceContent: Fischl Oz, my loyal companion. That we should have met this person, one who hails from another world as I do... Perhaps even cruel fate has deigned to smile upon me, though sin courses through my veins. If I am indeed destined to remain here, in this inescapable prison that is reality, at least—Oz I understand, mein Fräulein! In this traveler, Fräulein has found one who will never forsake her.

f5c5cfd35c881cc9.voiceContent: Fischl Ozvaldo von Hrafnavins. I, the Prinzessin der Verurteilung, sovereign of the Immernachtreich, do hereby call upon thee to do all within thy power to deliver the traveler from the claws of fate that would seek to snatch them at every turn, and to ready thy mind lest thou be required to make the ultimate sacrifice in the performance of this noblest of duties.Oz ...You'd place my life in danger so easily, mein Fräulein?

4dc6fb56de6b9f2d.voiceContent: Huh, you and I are both travelers from another world. That our paths have crossed here is no accident, but the will of fate.

c2ebae925cc6bba0.voiceContent: You seem... troubled. Traveler, do not lose heart! For with my left eye, the Auge der Verurteilung, which sees the threads of fate, I will surely keep you from harm. And Oz, the raven that has witnessed the demise of countless worlds, will watch over you on your journey. Should this world, like a beast prowling in the night, covet your dreams, then I, Prinzessin der Verurteilung, shall fell it with my ensorcelled arrows of judgment!

a34eef924c2dcfb7.voiceContent: Oh? You inquire about my Edelstein der Dunkelheit? It is a royal heirloom, a ceremonial ornament that displays the majesty of the Prinzessin der Verurteilung before the unworthy. Even here, in this fallen world, I have been reunited with my rightful inheritance as one of royal blood and noble spirit, for the majesty of a true princess shall draw her royal heirlooms unto her wherever so she may roam.

cb485e20735ad774.voiceContent: Fischl If one must reckon time as this world does, I, Fischl, have already seen three thousand winters. Not that the illusory passage of time has any bearing on one such as I, to whom the causality of three thousand universes has been unveiled.Oz Be that as it may, mein Fräulein, you are not yet considered to be of drinking age in this world, and no bartender can ever be convinced otherwise.

e19f3822d8fd349e.voiceContent: Oz's full name is Ozvaldo von Hrafnavins. Where I hail from, he holds dominion over star and sky across three universes, and the souls of the mighty, fallen in battle, rest in the shadow of his wings. One should add that the penalty for mispronouncing his name is to have one's tongue torn from one's mouth. However, as I am a princess and you are one who has my favor, we are at liberty to simply call him, Oz.

636467815a6bf73b.voiceContent: Fischl Ah, the ill-starred young man... My Auge der Verurteilung has seen with unmistakable clarity how his heart ails at being forsaken by the world—Oz Someone needs to keep an eye on the unlucky fellow.

08f7f57c79ac7e14.voiceContent: Fischl The magus-custodian of books, gatekeeper of universal knowledge... Win her trust, and one may yet gain access to a vast repository of wisdom...Oz She means as long as you return your first few library books on time, you'll never have any trouble borrowing a book again.

2a6677f424ce46e6.voiceContent: Fischl His nature is obscure, his fate a mystery, and his speech a vexing tapestry woven of both fact and fiction... Perhaps he and I share the burden of mystical sight...Oz Or perhaps he's secretly an actual pirate?

e985a2679bf5d4a6.voiceContent: Fischl Aha, yes, Mona, the mighty astrologer... Mona, who once had the vanity to probe the fate of the Prinzessin der Verurteilung herself! She wound up a trembling wreck, overborne and overmastered.Oz The poor lass was trying desperately not to laugh. It was no easy task.

5f367a95dbc4967e.voiceContent: Fischl One finds Sister Rosaria to be a most devout believer in the Anemo Archon.Oz ...Devout believer, mein Fräulein?Fischl Indeed! One night, I heard her invoking the name of the Archon thus in another's presence May you be struck down in the name of Lord Bartabos! One presumed that she was leading a prayer.

22ba05ca8b4e2fea.voiceContent: To condemn the guilty, to sanctify the just, and to draw all castaway dreams into the embrace of the infinite Immernachtreich. This is the birthright of the Prinzessin der Verurteilung, and her burden. None may gainsay it.

50aca3d17e416f6d.voiceContent: My left eye? It is the all-seeing Auge der Verurteilung, which reveals all that is true in the world. As to the question of why I conceal it... Well, would you willingly bear the agony of piercing to the heart of all truths? Furthermore... the world would lose much of its appeal if wholly stripped of delusion and falsehood.

e52e89da5f8823dc.voiceContent: Fischl Stormterror? Why, one never would have thought that a being that one might have kept as her pet could, in this world, be capable of causing such calamity. *sigh* Pitiable are the incompetents of this world...Oz That said, mein Fräulein, were you not beside yourself with worry for everyone's safety during said calamity?Fischl Th—That is because the Prinzessin der Verurteilung has the solemn duty to safeguard the souls of all, be they petty beings or not...

3f6a97e28e1d0f87.voiceContent: Oz Some people address her by other names. But to me, the one who gave me life and bestowed my powers upon me is Fischl, and none other. All things considered, Fischl is the name that most aptly captures her identity. Seriously, don't call her anything else, or—Fischl Oh, how one's royal ears do burn! Pray tell, what is the matter which you discuss so furtively?Oz Mid—Midnight Phantasmagoria, mein Fräulein! And... the majesty of the Verurteilung name!

e65875ec0a0a21fe.voiceContent: Why must the Prinzessin der Verurteilung punish sin? Because sin defies fate's rightful decree, of course! ...And of course, fate brought you here, so, so... Ahem! It was fate that saw to your descent upon this world, destiny that saw our paths intertwined. I, Fischl, shall always protect you. Because... because fate has revealed to me that this is what has been decreed!

8f1e1c27cc358652.voiceContent: I, Fischl, have roamed the galaxy and traversed countless worlds. I have learned the fate of ten thousand universes and have had revealed unto me the destiny of every living soul.

123b7a31338559b5.voiceContent: Oz Mein Fräulein reads a lot of novels. *sigh* My name, Oz, is from one of her favorites.

ebd7f63240b1606b.voiceContent: What does it take to rile a princess? ...If you must know, it is those who cannot recognize my true identity. But it is no great loss, for solitude is the noble's lot, so long as I do not lose the nobility of my soul...

a4349a36f8eb91b9.voiceContent: Fischl Hmph! What is food but the shackles of mortal flesh? ...But if the Prinzessin der Verurteilung should reckon any morsel worthy, then it must be the tears of sinners and the tongues of liars.Oz Has mein Fräulein lost her appetite for the Mitternachtsbrot des Sommernachtgartens?Fischl ...Uh— That is merely to provide mine earthly vessel with such sustenance as it doth require to perform its royal duties!

4b9ea84f65e493f6.voiceContent: Such an exquisite delicacy is worthy of being served in the Garten Sanssouci.

b1798c56a3d4c71c.voiceContent: To vanquish the Beast of the World, one must first rise above mundane desires, thus weaving the path that leads to destiny.

cb37060be8914750.voiceContent: Why dost thou insist on raining down chaos and destruction in the presence of your Prinzessin?

e1bb28b9596dd577.voiceContent: Fischl Well! If today is truly the anniversary of your birth, it shan't do for me not to mark the occasion. You have my full attention. Speak! Speak to me of your wishes, that which you most desire to fulfill during your fleeting and harsh existence in this wretched world. Whatever that wish may be. Even if, perchance—Oz She means, Happy Birthday, and if you want, she can—Fischl Silence, Oz.

e8a0a9800b251755.voiceContent: Fischl My magic arrow cries out my holy name as it streaks through the night, praying that the violet lightning of retribution shall strike the enemies of fate down from the skies!Oz Quite awe-inspiring, mein Fräulein! Since it's nearly dinner time, perhaps you might shoot a pigeon down while you're at it?

b6dacb7914f17072.voiceContent: Fischl With this, I may more fully manifest my majesty as Prinzessin der Verurteilung, and defeat that sworn enemy of fate named reality.Oz It will also be of use in your work for the Adventurers' Guild, mein Fräulein.

3c343d70d4a26ebb.voiceContent: Rejoice! Else, tremble in fear! Whenceforth springs this call to mirth and misery, you ask? Let it be known that I, the Prinzessin der Verurteilung, sovereign of the Immernachtreich, have peered forth with mine leftmost eye into the tapestry of fate that doth make up the universe, and beheld its every warp, weft and dangling orphaned thread!

2a4aefa9cd11fa88.voiceContent: I appear to have now regained most of the strength I lost in my transition to this world. Mwuhahaha, the day of judgment is nigh! ...Ah, worry not. Even at the last, when I bring the lightning of retribution upon this world, you shall come to no harm, for thou art blessed by the Prinzessin.

78ba8d0573d38ad1.voiceContent: Doth thou wish to witness my true power?

4a90befe80b0b72e.voiceContent: Oz Mein Fräulein! Should you fall...

cc4e20f63d50e237.voiceContent: This cruel fate befits not one of royal blood!

0838d71029884fdb.voiceContent: Oz I believe I know the answer to this one...Fischl Indeed you do, Oz! Ah, that poor mortal coil, mutilated by bondage unnatural...Oz It will never again fly as I do...Fischl Deprived of the humble coif with which it was born to gaze in awe at the majesty of its monarch... Surely it is a glimpse of my homeworld's hell, in the flesh. Hmm, the name of the dish escapes me...Oz Something something Madame, isn't it?

7c019b1581c5d280.voiceContent: Fischl Sweet shall be thy sleep, spared of the Mares of the Night! For no Night-Mares would dare draw near to those who are blessed by the Immernachtreich!Oz She means, Goodnight.

c16cdb2281b8dab2.voiceContent: Mein Fräulein does not care a great deal for this dish. My apologies.

51e7d7ce4907c3fc.voiceContent: Mein Fräulein says that she thoroughly enjoys your delicious cooking.

52692c24a58255f8.voiceContent: Why dost thou insist on raining down chaos and destruction in the presence of your Prinzessin?

689b5e0633d555f6.voiceContent: And yet, on this occasion, you appear to have eaten your fill, mein Fräulein.

2fc874058e8678ee.voiceContent: Such an exquisite delicacy is worthy of being served in the Garten Sanssouci.

1a405b332b367d14.voiceContent: To vanquish the Beast of the World, one must first rise above mundane desires, thus weaving the path that leads to destiny.

d560e588593979b3.voiceContent: Weep tears of joy, for you shall live to witness my majesty again!

acf81c19488c729f.voiceContent: For the Prinzessin blessed with this Auge der Verurteilung, a card game such as this is but a trivial matter.

16dde1a31c4a6e9c.voiceContent: Hm, hm, hm! Long have the forces of fate cascaded towards your doom.

d9558f8b07643ab3.voiceContent: Let the curtain of night descend, and place you into everlasting perdition!

1318605da0365cfc.voiceContent: This game is but threads of truth interwoven with a web of fiction, and I hold each strand between my fingertips.

13c6e6b68150a3b0.voiceContent: Arch-nemesis of the Prinzessin... How hast thou escaped the cascading forces of fate?

47631a58d9632fbc.voiceContent: Are you taking your leave? Just as well, for the Prinzessin is preparing to retire for the time being.

85c1fb9a3de6e32d.voiceContent: H—How did my Auge der Verurteilung fail to foresee this outcome?

12e937a06e1fad9c.voiceContent: Who invokes the holy name of the Prinzessin?

b6ea00cbe3dc9998.voiceContent: But a small thread in the grand tapestry of fate.

21750eb15842f31f.voiceContent: Fall before the curtain of night.

7ecb5c24d1b3a568.voiceContent: I strike down the foe of fate!

39ba15fb0ce1e535.voiceContent: The hour of Verurteilung is here!

17679c99f049f602.voiceContent: Surrender your soul to eternal shadow!

6432481286956446.voiceContent: Ugh... All shall change with the coming dawn!

e955aa0a4618b82f.voiceContent: ...You seek in vain to divert the course of destiny.
